Digital Ally Inc.


            
            Digital Ally, Inc. engages in designing and manufacturing of digital technology. It produces digital video imaging and storage products for use in law enforcement, fire, emergency medical services, security, and commercial fleet industries. The company's products include in-car audio and video recording equipment, body-worn cameras, cloud and local server software and storage solutions. Digital Ally was founded on December 13, 2000 and is headquartered in Lenexa, KS.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  




