VuLink®
Digital Ally's Patented Technology
VuLink® is the first product on the market to fully integrate in-car cameras and body worn video. The patented technology behind VuLink®; enables automatic activation of your in-car camera, wireless microphone and body-worn video camera.





View Flyer











Focus on the Job, not your video
Reduce Distractions
VuLink® wirelessly activates all of your Digital Ally™ video systems automatically and simultaneously by use of multiple triggers. 












Complete Solution
Learn more about our full collection of products to provide you with a complete solution.







