發佈日期：2015年8月26日VuLink is a hands-free body camera activation device that links with your Digital Ally in-car video system.  It enables an officer to automatically or manually start recordings on the FirstVu HD Body-Worn Video Systems and/or Digital Ally In-Car Video Systems simultaneously by utilizing customizable vehicle recording triggers.  Visit www.digitalallyinc.com for more information! 



